node.text:
Spotting sea snakes with @brodiemoss: “Sea snakes normally avoid humans but this time of year they become very active, sexually frustrated and potentially aggressive as they search for a mate 🐍 like this old fella who appeared from the ocean floor and followed me around on my paddle board before disappearing 😅”

What would you do in this situation? 😱

📽 @brodiemoss

node.text:
This kitty had very beautiful kittens. She fed them, cleaned them, kept them safe.
But one day all her kittens disappeared.
The thing is, that owners of mama-kitty gave her kittens to neighbors and friends, so all of them became adopted..
Mama-kitty did not know that! Disappearances of her kittens hit her tender heart very hard.
Her mind could not accepted that she lost all her daughters and sons.. and she replaced them with stuffed toys of her owners child.
Till now, she is trying to care about stuffed teddy bears as they are her own kittens, but she is doing that with one difference only. She never leave them alone even for one minute! This way she hope they will not disappear without a trace...😿

Share/TAG 🌟 friends whose cats already gave them kittens or will do that one day in the future ❤️❤️❤️
Each Like and Comment help to spread cuteness and pure joy through the universe! 😸

📸@atlas_scottish_fold #Animalonplanet
